name: Candy Jar of a Guitarist - Halloween Special
description:
When guitarists enter a music store, they get lost in the emotions that a child feels the moment they enter a candy store. They examine each guitar, look at the colorful pedals and want to buy one of each. Candies are the first thing that comes to my mind during Halloween. That's why I'm giving you a guitarist's candy jar.
